where $E_{\rm pol} = mc^2 = \hbar\nu_C$ is the compressive ZBW
polarization energy of the eDP cloud (ZBW Mass companion,
Proposition~4.1), $V_0 = \frac{4}{3}\pi\lP^3$ is the Voronoi cell volume,
and $\Delta\SSV_i$ is the SSV contribution from the $i$-th nearest-neighbor
