and Stiffness~$C$ companions.  No new postulate is required.
\end{proof}

The full LSP is therefore:
\begin{equation}
  \LSP \;=\; \Bigl(\mathbf{x}_{\rm GP},\; t_{\rm abs},\;
  mc^2/V_0,\; {\textstyle\sum_i}\,\hat{\mathbf{e}}_i\Delta\SSV_i\Bigr).
