%══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

\textbf{(1) Full nonlinear Einstein equations.}  Showing that the CPP
self-consistency condition reproduces the Ricci tensor and scalar of
differential geometry requires proving convergence of the discrete lattice
sum to a smooth Riemannian manifold.

\textbf{(2) Exact Schwarzschild solution.}  Solving the self-consistency
